reviews.review_text: Nice recording  Unfortunately a very lopsided show, with everyone playing like a champ but not really clicking. This is a 3 with points for hilarity, like Bobby interrupting the ill-fated Supplication instrumental with a horribly rushed Let It Griw, changing his mind too late, and then trying to go back into whatever remained of Supplication out of the end of Uncle John’s in the second set. 86 was a pretty funny year at times.
